    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and honestly, she still has that showroom glow. It\u2019s rare to find one kept this spotless\u2014the interior is pristine and she drives as smooth as silk. She\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and is just waiting for the right person to take her on her next adventure. I\u2019d love for her to go to someone who appreciates a truly well-cared-for ride. Come by, let's chat cars, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so head-over-heels for this one!",
      "price": 44500.0,
