    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-caliber example of the legendary S65-powered platform. This machine features a laser-straight chassis with zero-tolerance fitment across all panels. The naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 pulls with surgical precision, benefiting from upgraded rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure peak reciprocating assembly health. The DCT transmission has been flashed for lightning-fast shift logic, paired with a meticulously tuned suspension geometry that offers unparalleled turn-in response. Every fluid has been exchanged at half-intervals, and the thermal management system is optimized for peak performance. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically optimized masterpiece ready for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
