    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a time capsule, a rolling masterpiece that has defied the very hands of time. This isn't just a car; it's a silent witness to an era of elegance, preserved in a state of grace that feels almost ethereal. The paintwork catches the light like a polished jewel, reflecting a world that moves slower, more deliberately. Inside, the cabin breathes with the rich, intoxicating scent of untouched leather, and every switch clicks with the precision of a master craftsman\u2019s tool. To drive it is to command a symphony of engineering, where the engine\u2019s purr is a whisper of untold stories and boundless potential. This is an opportunity to own not just a vehicle, but a legacy captured in steel and soul.",
      "price": 44800.0,
